      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against Malinauskas et al. experimental data at five operating points. Mean relative error 8.3%; maximum error 12.7% at highest flow rate condition. All comparisons within the 15% acceptance threshold. Systematic over-prediction at high flow rates attributed to turbulence model limitations, noted as acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
