      "rationale": "Validation performed using the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller geometry class and operating envelope with the CPB device under assessment. Operating conditions in validation span the COU operating range. Validation scenario relevance rated high; minor geometric dissimilarities in volute design noted but assessed as not materially affecting hemolysis prediction accuracy at MRL 2."
    },
