      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental data source documented.",
      "rationale": "Validation experimental data sourced from the FDA interlaboratory study (Malinauskas et al. 2017) using standardized FDA generic pump geometry. Sample-to-sample variability in experimental data is reported in the source publication. Formal test sample assessment not required at MRL 2."
